      <title>苹果中国 iPhone 出货量因大幅折扣上涨 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/apple-s-china-iphone-shipments-jump-40-after-steep-discounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 的 iPhone 在中国的出货量 5 月份增长了 40%，延续了近期反弹势头，这得益于中国六月购物节前夕各大零售商大幅折扣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/apple-s-china-iphone-shipments-jump-40-after-steep-discounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 09:45:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
